[
  {
    "startTime": 1.51,
    "endTime": 3.5199999999999996,
    "text": "Who am I fooling?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.52,
    "endTime": 6.4510000000000005,
    "text": "It's going to take a miracle to get me into the army."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.451,
    "endTime": 8.93,
    "text": "Did I hear someone ask for a miracle?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.3,
    "endTime": 11.073,
    "text": "Let me hear you say ahh. - Ahh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.97,
    "endTime": 13.3,
    "text": "That's close enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.4,
    "endTime": 14.1,
    "text": "A ghost."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.1,
    "endTime": 17.297,
    "text": "Get ready Mulan. Your serpentine salvation is at hand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.297,
    "endTime": 23.2,
    "text": "For I have been sent by your ancestors to guide you to your masquerade."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.2,
    "endTime": 25.79,
    "text": "Come on, if you're gonna stay you're gonna work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.79,
    "endTime": 27.243,
    "text": "So heed my word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.243,
    "endTime": 32.272999999999996,
    "text": "'Cause if the army finds out you're a girl, the penalty is death."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.66,
    "endTime": 36.089999999999996,
    "text": "- Who are you? - Who am I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.09,
    "endTime": 40.75,
    "text": "Who am I? I am the guardian of lost souls."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.75,
    "endTime": 46.237,
    "text": "I am the powerful, the pleasurable, the indestructible, Mushu."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.575,
    "endTime": 52.357,
    "text": "Pretty hot, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.7,
    "endTime": 59.52,
    "text": "My ancestors sent a little lizard to help me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.52,
    "endTime": 62.75,
    "text": "Hey, dragon, dragon. Not lizard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.75,
    "endTime": 64.373,
    "text": "I don't do that tongue thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.36,
    "endTime": 69.783,
    "text": "No, no, no. Put me down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.783,
    "endTime": 73.5,
    "text": "Stop it. No. Let me go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.5,
    "endTime": 75.033,
    "text": "Give me him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.745,
    "endTime": 78.686,
    "text": "Stop. Stop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.4,
    "endTime": 89.295,
    "text": "Easy boy. Easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.295,
    "endTime": 90.738,
    "text": "Settle down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.007,
    "endTime": 97.007,
    "text": "Easy boy. Easy. Easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.224,
    "endTime": 98.057,
    "text": "That's it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.43,
    "endTime": 103.263,
    "text": "Now sit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.83,
    "endTime": 105.693,
    "text": "Sit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.56,
    "endTime": 107.393,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.393,
    "endTime": 109.06,
    "text": "Now drop the boot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.06,
    "endTime": 109.973,
    "text": "Drop it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.2,
    "endTime": 115.382,
    "text": "Oh you're such a good boy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.382,
    "endTime": 118.9,
    "text": "Yes you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 122.64,
    "text": "You all tired from chasing this bad man all over the place?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.64,
    "endTime": 123.71,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.71,
    "endTime": 126.57,
    "text": "Nobody appreciates you, do they?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.57,
    "endTime": 127.86999999999999,
    "text": "Do they?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.87,
    "endTime": 128.76,
    "text": "Oh, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.76,
    "endTime": 130.06,
    "text": "He's a bad horse."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.06,
    "endTime": 132.683,
    "text": "Oh, he's nothing but a big sweetheart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.79,
    "endTime": 136.793,
    "text": "Isn't that right? Maximus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.01,
    "endTime": 139.623,
    "text": "You got to be kidding me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.72,
    "endTime": 143.92,
    "text": "Last time I introduce myself, my name Raymond."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.92,
    "endTime": 145.64399999999998,
    "text": "But if I call me Rick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.644,
    "endTime": 149.0,
    "text": "Pardon me but your accent, it's funny, no?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 151.34,
    "text": "Well, I'm a cajun, bro."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.34,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Born and bred in the bayou."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.0,
    "endTime": 155.64,
    "text": "Yall must be new around here, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.64,
    "endTime": 160.26999999999998,
    "text": "Actually, we are from a place far, far away from this world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.27,
    "endTime": 162.193,
    "text": "Go to bed. Y'all from Shreveport?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.167,
    "endTime": 167.0,
    "text": "No, no, no. We are people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.0,
    "endTime": 171.34,
    "text": "Prince Charming here got himself turned into a frog by Voodoo witch doctor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.34,
    "endTime": 172.861,
    "text": "Well there you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.98,
    "endTime": 177.773,
    "text": "- Who is it? - Mrs. Potts, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.2,
    "endTime": 182.14,
    "text": "I thought you might like a spot of tea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.14,
    "endTime": 183.54999999999998,
    "text": "But you're a..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.55,
    "endTime": 185.095,
    "text": "You're..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.928,
    "endTime": 186.87,
    "text": "Careful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.87,
    "endTime": 188.3,
    "text": "This is impossible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.3,
    "endTime": 191.04000000000002,
    "text": "I know it is, but here we are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.04,
    "endTime": 193.92,
    "text": "Told ya' she was pretty mama, didn't I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.92,
    "endTime": 196.33999999999997,
    "text": "All right, Chip, now that'll do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.34,
    "endTime": 198.323,
    "text": "Slowly now. Dont spill."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.58,
    "endTime": 201.16000000000003,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.16,
    "endTime": 202.633,
    "text": "Want to see me do a trick?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.64,
    "endTime": 205.94,
    "text": "Chip."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.94,
    "endTime": 207.5,
    "text": "Oops. Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.5,
    "endTime": 210.32,
    "text": "That was a very brave thing you did my dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.32,
    "endTime": 211.6,
    "text": "We all think so."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.6,
    "endTime": 215.46,
    "text": "But I've lost my father, my dreams, everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.46,
    "endTime": 220.21,
    "text": "Cheer up, child. It'll turn out all right in the end."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.21,
    "endTime": 221.71,
    "text": "You'll see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.71,
    "endTime": 225.76000000000002,
    "text": "Oh, listen to me, jabbering on while there's a supper to get on the table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.76,
    "endTime": 226.643,
    "text": "Chip."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.767,
    "endTime": 228.73,
    "text": "Bye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.73,
    "endTime": 229.593,
    "text": "You're right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.83,
    "endTime": 235.11,
    "text": "You aren't just some price to be won."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.11,
    "endTime": 238.02,
    "text": "You should be free to make your own choice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.02,
    "endTime": 239.359,
    "text": "I'll go now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.359,
    "endTime": 240.192,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.192,
    "endTime": 241.77100000000002,
    "text": "What? What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.771,
    "endTime": 245.04999999999998,
    "text": "How are you doing that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.05,
    "endTime": 246.17000000000002,
    "text": "It's a magic carpet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.17,
    "endTime": 247.783,
    "text": "It's lovely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.34,
    "endTime": 253.89000000000001,
    "text": "You don't want to go for a ride, do you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.89,
    "endTime": 256.81,
    "text": "We could get out of the palace. See the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.81,
    "endTime": 257.87,
    "text": "Is it safe?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.87,
    "endTime": 259.07,
    "text": "Sure, do you trust me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.934,
    "endTime": 262.1,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.1,
    "endTime": 263.178,
    "text": "Do you trust me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.908,
    "endTime": 355.3,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.3,
    "endTime": 356.466,
    "text": "Moana."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.0,
    "endTime": 376.821,
    "text": "- How about a little less pigging and a..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.037,
    "endTime": 379.69,
    "text": "I know that tune."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.69,
    "endTime": 381.779,
    "text": "Dippermouth blues."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.14,
    "endTime": 387.368,
    "text": "Play it, brother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.61,
    "endTime": 392.89300000000003,
    "text": "Oh, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.2,
    "endTime": 398.3,
    "text": "Where you've been all my life?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.4,
    "endTime": 400.35999999999996,
    "text": "Where did you learn to play like that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.36,
    "endTime": 403.07,
    "text": "Well, the Bayou's is the best jazz school in the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.07,
    "endTime": 404.94,
    "text": "All the greats play the river boats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.94,
    "endTime": 409.8,
    "text": "Oh, Louis give anything to be up there jamming with the big boys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.8,
    "endTime": 410.83,
    "text": "Why don't you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.83,
    "endTime": 412.48199999999997,
    "text": "Oh, I tried once."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 423.271,
    "endTime": 425.0,
    "text": "It didn't end well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.0,
    "endTime": 426.018,
    "text": "Oh, dear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.934,
    "endTime": 431.434,
    "text": "I wonder if the children are--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.0,
    "endTime": 450.2,
    "text": "Why you're little men."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.2,
    "endTime": 455.263,
    "text": "How do you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.397,
    "endTime": 458.56,
    "text": "I said how do you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.56,
    "endTime": 460.7,
    "text": "How do you do what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.7,
    "endTime": 463.64,
    "text": "Oh, you can talk. I'm so glad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.64,
    "endTime": 465.8,
    "text": "Now don't tell me who you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.8,
    "endTime": 466.913,
    "text": "Let me guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.36,
    "endTime": 469.63,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 469.63,
    "endTime": 470.641,
    "text": "You're Doc."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.641,
    "endTime": 475.0,
    "text": "Oh, why, yes. Yes, that's true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.0,
    "endTime": 478.79,
    "text": "And you're-- - You're Bashful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.79,
    "endTime": 481.89700000000005,
    "text": "Oh, gosh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.616,
    "endTime": 486.798,
    "text": "And you? You're Sleepy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.798,
    "endTime": 487.981,
    "text": "How'd you guess?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.348,
    "endTime": 492.515,
    "text": "And you're--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.46,
    "endTime": 496.565,
    "text": "You're Sneezy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.1,
    "endTime": 503.72700000000003,
    "text": "Yes. And you must be..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.727,
    "endTime": 504.79999999999995,
    "text": "Happy, ma'am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 504.8,
    "endTime": 505.63300000000004,
    "text": "That's me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.633,
    "endTime": 506.85999999999996,
    "text": "And this is Dopey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.86,
    "endTime": 509.017,
    "text": "He don't talk none."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.017,
    "endTime": 510.04,
    "text": "You mean he can't talk?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.04,
    "endTime": 511.20000000000005,
    "text": "He don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.2,
    "endTime": 512.435,
    "text": "He never tried."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.435,
    "endTime": 517.435,
    "text": "Oh, that's too bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.674,
    "endTime": 522.0,
    "text": "Oh, you must be Grumpy."
  }
]